title: Ryan Beat launches his Pro-Lite race truck to a Podium Finish
description: Team Gibson racer, Ryan Beat had a solid race weekend at Lucas Oil Off-Road in Arizona taking hisRockstar Energy powered Pro-Lite to a podium finish and earning Fastest Lap.   The great results of the weekend have Ryan Beat starting the season in 2nd, just shy off the leader.
